<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«è¨ˆç®—ã•ã‚Œã¾ã™ã€‚ä»¥é™ã®è¨ˆç®—ã§ã¯ç°¡å˜ã®ãŸã‚ã€æ³¢æ•°ãƒ™ã‚¯ãƒˆãƒ«ã‚’\(\mathbf{k} = (k_x, 0, 0)\)ã¨ã—ã¦è¨ˆç®—ã‚’è¡Œã„ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚(8)å¼ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[i\omega \Sigma_1 + \Sigma_0 (-i \mathbf{k}) \cdot \mathbf{v}_1 = 0 \ \Longrightarrow \ 
\omega\delta \Sigma - \Sigma_0 k_x \delta v_x 
= 0 \tag{13}\]

<p>(9)å¼ã‹ã‚‰</p>

\[\Sigma_0 i \omega \mathbf{v}_1 
= - C_s^2 (-i \mathbf{k}) \Sigma_1 - \Sigma_0 \nabla \Phi_1 - 2\Sigma_0 \Omega \mathbf{e}_z \times \mathbf{v}_1 
= i C_s^2 \Sigma_1 \mathbf{k} + \Sigma_0 \frac{2\pi G}{k} (|k|) (-i \mathbf{k}) \Sigma_1 - 2\Sigma_0 \Omega \mathbf{e}_z \times \mathbf{v}_1\]

